### What do you go by / What are your common aliases?
4554551N-533K3R Ph@nt0m5tr1k3r
### What are your skill sets?
Coding: C, C++, Python, Golang, Assembly, Java, Perl, PHP, Rust Reverse Engineering Exploit Development Pen Testing/Hacking Security Architecture GRC
### What are you interested in?
All of the above. I am on a never ending quest to increase my knowledge and refine my skills and tool sets.

### How’d you find us?
